[Student "S"]
{NORTH wants to be in game but doesn't know which one. 
If SOUTH holds three \Hs she would prefer 4\H, 
otherwise she would try 3NT. NORTH bids 2\S, Fourth Suit Forcing.

SOUTH denies three \Hs but confirms a \S honor by 
bidding 2NT, so NORTH bids the game in Notrump.}

